<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2204] Localization causes a problem in WebConsole configuration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2204</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After implementing &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2203&quot; title=&quot;provide localization of plugin titles&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FELIX-2203&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FELIX-2203&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; when opening the apache web console configuration, the titles are shown with their resource names, not their real names.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
